      "blocks": {
        "rich_text_hbPJDz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When the ring in question is your <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Engagement Ring</span></a>, it’s way more than just an accessory. An Engagement Ring is probably one of the most priceless things you’ll ever own for all the right reasons. From marking your special day to carrying the message of your everlasting love, an Engagement ring weighs much more in terms of sentimental value. </p><p>But as the years go by and your story grows richer, your style might also evolve. Maybe your original ring no longer matches who you are today, or maybe it’s simply time to add a fresh sparkle to the love that still shines strong.</p><p>That’s where resetting your Engagement Ring comes in. And if you're considering an upgrade, Lab Grown Diamonds are making that decision smarter, more ethical, and beautifully accessible.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_XBeY84": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why People Upgrade Their Engagement Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why People Upgrade Their Engagement Rings</h2>",
            "custom_id": "upgrade",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_VwiqGC": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Why_do_people_upgrade.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Upgrading doesn’t really mean replacing your original ring. Rather, it’s about adding a fresh touch to the original ring in order to give it an instant uplift. Some couples upgrade for a milestone anniversary or after a major life event, while others simply want to refresh their ring to better reflect their current style. It’s often a celebration of years spent together, of personal growth, or of reaching a new chapter in life. </p><p>Common reasons for upgrading include:</p><ul><li>Opting for a more sustainable, eco-conscious option like a Lab Grown Diamond</li><li>Wanting a larger or more brilliant diamond</li><li>Changing the setting style (e.g., from yellow gold to platinum)</li><li>Adding new elements like a halo, side stones, or custom engravings </li></ul><p>Whatever your reason, the process of resetting your Engagement Ring can be incredibly meaningful and fun!</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "1-50-ct-emerald-solitaire-halo-diamond-ring",
              "0-91ct-round-diamond-channel-eternity-band"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qT84a3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Choose a Lab Grown Diamond for the Upgrade?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Choose a Lab Grown Diamond for the Upgrade?</h2><p>The physical structure, molecular makeup and visual appearance of Lab Grown Diamonds match those of natural Mined Diamonds. The only distinctive factor is their origin. Advanced technology in Lab settings produces sustainable and conflict-free diamonds that offer better affordability.</p><p>Lab Grown Diamonds now gain popularity for ring resets because of these key reasons:</p>",
            "custom_id": "labgrown",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_y6fAVe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>1. More Diamond for Your Budget</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_wHVkPU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": ". More Diamond for Your Budget",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1080_x_400_More_Diamond_for_your_budget.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Lab Grown Diamonds have price tags that fall between 30% and 40% below traditional Mined Diamond costs. With Lab Grown Diamonds, you have the flexibility to get a larger diamond or better clarity grade, or a more elegant cut shape without exceeding your spending limit.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Xp9DAm": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Sustainable and Ethical",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>2. Sustainable and Ethical</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_pwjVAX": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Sustainable and Ethical",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sustainability_1080_500.jpg",
            "text": "<p>As you grow, your sense of ethics and responsibility also evolves. If you are someone who values environmental wellbeing and ethics, this is your chance to make a conscious choice by ditching mined diamonds for the sustainable lab grown versions. Lab grown diamonds come with the assurance that there is no significant environmental or ethical concern.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Nr8Mgw": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "3. Customization Freedom",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>3. Customization Freedom</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_GeBA9f": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "3. Customization Freedom",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/500_500_Bespoken.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Lab Grown Diamond opens the door to a whole world of possibilities. No longer limited by the scarcity or high cost of traditionally mined stones, a Lab Grown Diamond gives you the freedom to dream bigger and design bolder. Whether it's exploring rare and vibrant colors like blush pinks, icy blues, or canary yellows or opting for unique, non-traditional cuts such as elongated cushions, geometric shapes, or even custom silhouettes what was once out of reach is now beautifully accessible.</p><p>You’re no longer designing within limitations. With a Lab Grown Diamond, you can play with scale, personalize every detail, and express your style without compromise. From modern minimalism to intricate vintage inspired pieces, the flexibility and affordability these stones offer let you create jewelry that’s not only stunning, but also deeply personal.</p><p>And the best part? You can do it all with a clear conscience, knowing your Lab Grown Diamond is sustainably made, conflict-free, and better for the planet.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_XcnVWL": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Reset Your Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Reset Your Engagement Ring</h2><p>Resetting doesn’t mean starting from scratch. In fact, many couples choose to keep part of the original ring, like the band or accent stones, and just swap the centre diamond. Others use the existing materials to create a completely new design while holding on to the sentimental foundation of the original piece.</p><p>Here’s how the process generally works:</p>",
            "custom_id": "reset",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_N9Kxkq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Evaluate Your Current Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 1: Evaluate Your Current Ring</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_y4HeQK": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Step 1: Evaluate Your Current Ring",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1080_300_Step_1_Evaluate_Your_Current_Ring_Updated.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Look at the condition of your existing ring. Can the band be reused? Are the prongs or settings still secure? A jeweler can inspect the ring and let you know what’s possible.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-30-cts-marquise-solitaire-diamond-ring",
