            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Hr8Ez6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choose Your Lab Grown Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 2: Choose Your Lab Grown Diamond</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WtrhNc": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Step 2: Choose Your Lab Grown Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1080_500_Choose_Your_Lab_Grown_Diamond_Updated.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Consider what’s important to you: size, shape, brilliance, or price. Whether you're going for a classic round cut, a vintage-inspired cushion cut, or a trendy oval diamond, Lab Grown Diamonds offer a wide range of options with impressive clarity and sparkle.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_WWPfgb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 3: Pick Your New Setting</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ctbVhd": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Step 3: Pick Your New Setting",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Pick_Your_New_Setting_1080_600.jpg",
            "text": "<p>You can retain the original setting or go for a brand-new design. Some popular choices for upgraded rings include:</p><ul><li>Halo settings: Surround the centre diamond with a ring of smaller diamonds for added sparkle.</li><li>Three-stone rings: Symbolize your past, present, and future.</li><li>Solitaires: Clean, timeless, and effortlessly elegant.</li><li>Vintage settings: With milgrain details, filigree, or rose-cut diamonds for a romantic touch.</li></ul>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_YpE8Ea": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Step 4: Work With a Trusted Jeweler",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 4: Work With a Trusted Jeweler</h3><p>Partner with a jeweler who understands both the emotional and technical aspects of resetting an Engagement Ring. Ask questions, explore mock-ups, and make sure you're involved every step of the way.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_n7xJHt": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What to Do with the Original Diamond?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What to Do with the Original Diamond?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "original",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ibHYEX": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_to_Do_with_the_Original_Diamond_1080_400.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Upgrading doesn’t mean your original diamond has to sit in a drawer forever. There are several ways to keep it meaningful:</p><ul><li>Set it into a pendant or a pair of earrings</li><li>Use it in a promise ring for a child or family heirloom</li><li>Trade it in to offset the cost of the new ring</li><li>Keep it safe for future redesigns or upgrades</li></ul>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Y9aJcX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Fresh Sparkle for a Timeless Bond",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>A Fresh Sparkle for a Timeless Bond</h2><p>An Engagement Ring upgrade isn’t about replacing the past, it’s about celebrating the journey. Whether it’s ten years down the line or just a few, resetting your ring with a Lab Grown Diamond is a beautiful way to mark how far you’ve come and where you’re going together.</p><p>With ethical beauty, affordability, and endless custom options, Lab Grown Diamonds are not just a practical choice, they’re a powerful expression of modern love.</p><p>So, if you’re ready for a change, don’t be afraid to give your Engagement Ring the glow-up it deserves. Because your love has evolved, and your ring can, too.</p>",
            "custom_id": "fresh",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
